00:11:26.019 --> 00:11:32.659
displayed a specific quality in the ministry. The lessons will help us see how we can imitate

00:11:32.659 --> 00:11:39.779
the qualities they demonstrated as we make disciples. Each lesson contains a video that brings

00:11:39.779 --> 00:12:01.889
the account to life. A woman of Samaria came to draw water. Give me a drink. By cultivating an

00:12:01.889 --> 00:12:09.470
interest in people, we can talk about things that are on their minds. What truths might we share

00:12:09.470 --> 00:12:16.750
