00:12:16.750 --> 00:12:23.870
teach. Make it your goal to learn these basic truths and the scriptures that support them.

00:12:24.830 --> 00:12:30.590
If you do, you will be more effective in starting conversations and in making disciples.

00:12:31.309 --> 00:12:36.669
For example, a conversation can be started by asking a simple question, such as,

00:12:37.389 --> 00:12:45.309
have you heard that God will soon end all suffering? Or did you know that the earth's environment

00:12:45.309 --> 00:12:57.250
will be restored? Sharing a simple truth at the right time is powerful. Jesus said his sheep would

00:12:57.250 --> 00:13:03.970
listen to his voice. In other words, rightly disposed ones will recognize the truth when they hear

00:13:04.049 --> 00:13:11.009
