00:14:10.429 --> 00:14:17.389
By focusing on people, we will become more comfortable and more effective as we make disciples.

00:14:19.740 --> 00:14:25.259
As you consider each lesson, think carefully about how you can demonstrate the highlighted

00:14:25.259 --> 00:14:32.700
qualities when conversing with people in your community. Ask yourself, what are their concerns and

00:14:32.700 --> 00:14:40.700
needs? As you go about your activities, be observant. Look for appropriate opportunities to

00:14:40.700 --> 00:14:47.899
help people in practical ways. Acts of kindness can open the door to share kingdom truth.

00:14:49.580 --> 00:14:53.899
Show that you care by listening to others when they express themselves.

00:14:54.860 --> 00:15:04.139
Share a simple truth at the right time. Remember, our goal is not to memorize the presentation,

00:15:04.139 --> 00:15:10.620
but to demonstrate Christ-like love to everyone we meet. This will require patience,

00:15:13.169 --> 00:15:24.980
