00:15:25.539 --> 00:15:37.009
simply showing love will help us to find joy in our ministry. More than any specific technique,

00:15:37.730 --> 00:15:43.250
actively expressing our love for others will help us make disciples.

00:16:05.889 --> 00:16:13.730
